  <worksheets>
    <worksheet name='System Trace'>
      <layout-options>
        <title>
          <formatted-text>
            <run>One query through the system: five transitions</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </title>
        <caption>
          <formatted-text>
            <run>A single GPT-4o (Aug) long-prompt query (≈2.22 Wh) routed to AWS US East (Virginia) is traced through five transitions to atmospheric emissions. Blue bars carry energy (Wh); orange bars carry carbon (gCO₂e). Width is proportional to flow value, which is why the bottom two bars are visibly narrower — the unit conversion happens at the Virginia grid stage, where 2025 grid intensity (327 gCO₂/kWh, Ember) converts the 2.22 Wh of inference energy into ≈0.73 gCO₂e of emissions. The derived figure is within −3.8% of Jegham et al.&apos;s published 0.755 gCO₂e for the same query, a gap that reflects more current grid data in the integration than in the snapshot&apos;s static CIF assumption (0.34 vs Virginia&apos;s actual 0.327).</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </caption>
      </layout-options>
      <table>
        <view>
          <datasources>
            <datasource caption='c8_flow' name='federated.0z13vzl0colqym11nmoy50vqe4b5' />
          </datasources>
          <datasource-dependencies datasource='federated.0z13vzl0colqym11nmoy50vqe4b5'>
            <column-instance column='[flow_label]' derivation='Attribute' name='[attr:flow_label:nk]' pivot='key' type='nominal' />
            <column-instance column='[unit]' derivation='Attribute' name='[attr:unit:nk]' pivot='key' type='nominal' />
            <column caption='Flow Label' datatype='string' name='[flow_label]' role='dimension' type='nominal' />
            <column-instance column='[source]' derivation='None' name='[none:source:nk]' pivot='key' type='nominal' />
            <column-instance column='[target]' derivation='None' name='[none:target:nk]' pivot='key' type='nominal' />
            <column caption='Source' datatype='string' name='[source]' role='dimension' type='nominal' />
            <column-instance column='[value]' derivation='Sum' name='[sum:value:qk]' pivot='key' type='quantitative' />
            <column caption='Target' datatype='string' name='[target]' role='dimension' type='nominal' />
            <column caption='Unit' datatype='string' name='[unit]' role='dimension' type='nominal' />
            <column caption='Value' datatype='real' name='[value]' role='measure' type='quantitative' />
          </datasource-dependencies>
          <manual-sort column='[federated.0z13vzl0colqym11nmoy50vqe4b5].[none:source:nk]' direction='ASC'>
            <dictionary>
              <bucket>&quot;1 query&quot;</bucket>
              <bucket>&quot;GPT-4o (Aug) inference&quot;</bucket>
